sAuthor: Grande, M. d. C.[Maria del Carmen]
Citation.sAbstract: Density and viscosity of (water + dimethylsulphoxide) were measured precisely over the whole composition range at T = (298.15,  303.15, 308.15, 313.15, and 318.15) K. Differences between values from different authors are clarified and more reliable partial molar  volumes are obtained.
Citation.sTitle: On the density and viscosity of (water + dimethylsulphoxide) binary mixtures
